    How to Eliminate Noise Pollution
    With the fast development of national economy,more and more city dwellers suffer
from noise pollution,which causes health problem,If we ever want to solve this problem,
the overall planning of the government and the cooperation of all citizens are both need.
    On the one hand,major factories,as main noise creators,should be moved to
indusrial zones in suburbs.Department stores and big restaurants should not be
established too close to residential quarters.On the other hand,the municipal government
should gradually increase the ratio of green land in the city,which can reduce all
kinds of noises significantly.Moreover,all urban constructions should be stopped during
the night so as not to disturb the neighboring dwellers.
    All in all,only when all of us join in the efforts of eliminating noise pollution at
all levels can we hope to solve the noise problem satisfactority.
    